Companion code for submission # 1141 for CHI 2018
Awe the Audience: How Emotional Trajectories Affect Audience Perception in Public Speaking

Installation Instruction
========================
1. For python distribution, you can install anaconda or miniconda
https://conda.io/docs/user-guide/install/index.html

2. Install the requirements:
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. (Optional) If you want to extract IBM tone analyzer scores yourself:
# install it according to instructions given here: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/watson-developer-cloud
# Typically the following command should work (assumes pip):
# pip install --upgrade watson-developer-cloud

Usage
=====
cd tedanalytics
python ted_talk_experiments.py

Documentation
=============
All the codes are documented inline
